{"tid":121550,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"基沙文：英國天氣唔啱我！","createTime":"2017-02-15T10:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T02:32:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e4a6ffbacfc3f6c18382b257ee232dca291ce4b","tid":121550,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sports.now.com/sport/news/6/566/17335130566/17339941445_600x412.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F6%2F566%2F17335130566%2F17339941445_600x412.jpg&h=2758b3ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=58698644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】外界盛傳曼聯對馬德里體育會前鋒基沙文虎視眈眈，有意於夏季轉會窗將其帶往奧脫福，不過基沙文似乎對英超不感興趣，直指英國的天氣不適合自己。<br />\n<br />\n近年來，每逢轉會窗開啟都會有馬德里體育會前鋒基沙文（Antoine Griezmann）的轉會傳聞，而曼聯自摩連奴執過教鞭以後，對這名25歲法國前鋒的追求更為熱烈。基沙文接受西班牙傳媒訪問時，直言曾萌生離隊的想法：「早前和皇家蘇斯達比賽完之後，曾經認為自己需要離開，但現在已經沒有這個想法。大家都不知道賽季完結時的情況，或許屆時會重新審視自己，不過與現在竟無關係。」<br />\n<br />\n據悉，除了曼聯之外，英超球隊還有車路士希望引入基沙文，後者表示喜歡英超的比賽節奏，惟球場外的問題就成為了障礙：「如果我選擇了離隊，西班牙球會有巴塞隆拿和皇家馬德里，巴塞擁有三叉戟，而根據和馬體會的約定，我是不會轉投皇馬；德國的錦標並不吸引我，現在又不是回歸法國的時候；英格蘭方面，當地很多人會質疑我的私人生活，加上不時下雨等壞天氣&hellip;我確實需要在外玩樂放鬆。」<br />\n<br />\n基沙文球技出色人所共知，不過加盟條件多多，青睞他的球會似乎要加多把勁，才能吸引這名射手來投。"},{"pid":"3a7ac9e399ed08022a5e26f2ecac872c1b59485f","tid":121550,"uid":490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:41:49.000Z","msg":"扭屎忽花，嫌工嫌四，去中超賺人民幣啦"},{"pid":"efaf854453a6b939a1113ebdf31ec517bdbfdcfb","tid":121550,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扭屎忽花，嫌工嫌四，去中超賺人民幣啦</blockquote><br />\n基沙文：中國天氣啱我！"},{"pid":"38e9a11059e98803e21b827ac2241e3e276e9194","tid":121550,"uid":81037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>扭屎忽花，嫌工嫌四，去中超賺人民幣啦</blockquote><br />\n基沙文：中國天氣啱我！</blockquote><br />\n中國空氣啱我！"},{"pid":"d330513bb59472415643cd4ab79d65f0d4823373","tid":121550,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:06:56.000Z","msg":"拒絕我獌冇好下場"},{"pid":"26bc4867002702b5f87098424a1ad08a9114ab42","tid":121550,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"想要35萬磅一星期咪出聲"},{"pid":"da98facdb3ac5bc565d26785a0297433cedfcd86","tid":121550,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想要35萬磅一星期咪出聲</blockquote><br />\n少過50直接唔睇la下話，會少過泰維斯？"},{"pid":"db131a4d6e996bf4c3de908062ae13ff6b5aaa2d","tid":121550,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T11:48:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17368523460eb9f42dd6b4941e614048f55d04d3","tid":121550,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"今年唔黎姐<br />\n遲早都會黎架啦"},{"pid":"996796d32a9f2afae3f266a23bf50ecc8273bbe1","tid":121550,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:04:50.000Z","msg":"死獌狗又要轉J 邊個？"},{"pid":"d5ef91e700c95af630dea8b797021cccee984f42","tid":121550,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"咁似fifa career mode會講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdfe4069fe7c8a787d4c755cf59628d93a4c704","tid":121550,"uid":72712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁似fifa career mode會講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常講呢啲嘅球員俾多啲錢就仆嚟㗎啦<br />\n想要錢咪出聲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67491da902964002f62082814eaec4069e5e629e","tid":121550,"uid":75543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02